**To download the Rmarkdown file** for this tutorial within Open on Demand, you can use the following lines:  
```r
library(httr)
tutorial_name <- '{{ file }}'
GET(paste0('{{ file_path }}',tutorial_name), 
    write_disk(tutorial_name))
```
